features.text:
For decades now, our planet has been ruled by vicious AI overlords. ☠️


But some ingenious degens managed to develop camouflages to blend in with the evil robots. We call these camouflages: **BlockBots**! 

Click on the BlockBot & join the fight against the AI overlords. ✊

**BlockBots** **PowerUps**

From left to right

  | Weapon        | Descr.|
  | --------- |:-------:|
  | #1     | Sledge Hammer  |
  | #2     | Lunula Axe |
  | #3     | Gold Desert Eagle |
 | #4     | Deadly Knife       |
 | #5     | Knife of Chaos      |  
 | #6     | Warrior Staff      |

BlockBots Undergound Movement.

Prepare for battle.
